@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    #intro-container {
      background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.8), rgba(0,0,0,0.8)),
        url("https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original//s3TBrRGB1iav7gFOCNx3H31MoES.jpg");
    }

    #review-buy-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    #review-button, #buy-button {
      border: 1px solid;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 5% 0 5% auto;
      width: 70%;
    }

    #review-button {
      color: white;
    }

    #buy-button {
      background-color: white;
    }

    #cast-container {
      margin-left: 10%;
    }

    #cast-container img {
      border-radius: 50%;
      padding: 0;
    }

    #cast-container .col-7 {
      padding-left: 10%;
    }

    #detail-container {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    #detail-container h4 {
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);
      padding: 4% 0 2% 0;
    }

    .list-group-flush {
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .list-group-item {
      background: none;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container-fluid">
  <div id="intro-container" class="row">
    <div class="col-4" style="text-align: center">
      <img src="https://image.tmdb.org//t//p//w342////9gk7adHYeDvHkCSEqAvQNLV5Uge.jpg" style="max-width: 50%"/>
    </div>
    <div class="col-5">
      <h1 style="color: white">Inception</h1>
      <div id="tagline" style="color: darkgrey">Your mind is the scene of the crime.</div>
      <div>
        <span style="color: darkgrey">148m | 2010</span>
        <span id="genre-container">
          <span class="badge bg-secondary">Adventure</span>
          <span class="badge bg-secondary">Action</span>
          <span class="badge bg-secondary">Science Fiction</span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="badge bg-success">8.9</div>
      <div id="overview" style="color: white">Cobb, a skilled thief who commits corporate espionage by infiltrating the subconscious of his
        targets is offered a chance to regain his old life as payment for a task considered to be impossible:
        "inception", the implantation of another person's idea into a target's subconscious.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-3" id="review-buy-container">
      <div id="review-button" class="button">REVIEW</div>
      <div id="buy-button" class="button">BUY $9.90</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="detail-container" class="row">
    <div id="movie-fact-container" class="col-4" style="background-color: #eeeeee">
      <h4>MOVIE FACTS</h4>
      <ul class="list-group-flush">
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Release Date
          <span class="badge bg-dark">Jul 15, 2010</span>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Run Time
          <span class="badge bg-dark">148 m</span>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Box Office
          <span class="badge bg-dark">$825,532,634.00</span>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Budget
          <span class="badge bg-dark">$160,000,000.00</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h4>Trailers</h4>
      <div>Inception</div>
    </div>
    <div id="cast-container" class="col-5">
      <h4>CAST</h4>
      <ul class="list-group-flush">
        <li class="list-group-item row">
          <div class="row">
            <img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w342//wo2hJpn04vbtmh0B9utCFdsQhxM.jpg" class="col-1"/>
            <div class="col-7">Leonardo DiCaprio</div>
            <div class="col-4">Dom Cobb</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item row">
          <div class="row">
            <img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w342//psAXOYp9SBOXvg6AXzARDedNQ9P.jpg" class="col-1"/>
            <div class="col-7">Ken Watanabe</div>
            <div class="col-4">Mr. Saito</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item row">
          <div class="row">
            <img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w342//4U9G4YwTlIEbAymBaseltS38eH4.jpg" class="col-1"/>
            <div class="col-7">Joseph Gordon-Levitt</div>
            <div class="col-4">Arthur</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item row">
          <div class="row">
            <img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w342//zChwjQ9D90fxx6cgWz5mUWHNd5b.jpg" class="col-1"/>
            <div class="col-7">Marion Cotillard</div>
            <div class="col-4">Mal Cobb</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item row">
          <div class="row">
            <img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w342//tp157uXeMPA5G91cfecBWO2OFzn.jpg" class="col-1"/>
            <div class="col-7">Elliot Page</div>
            <div class="col-4">Ariadne</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item row">
          <div class="row">
            <img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w342//yVGF9FvDxTDPhGimTbZNfghpllA.jpg" class="col-1"/>
            <div class="col-7">Tom Hardy</div>
            <div class="col-4">Zak Eames</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item row">
          <div class="row">
            <img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w342//rm4jns47kaqh7oC7RYiXrESlVbV.jpg" class="col-1"/>
            <div class="col-7">Cillian Murphy</div>
            <div class="col-4">Robert Fischer</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item row">
          <div class="row">
            <img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w342//zLxzAdAfu7y02yEx29JSLDgXJZ4.jpg" class="col-1"/>
            <div class="col-7">Tom Berenger</div>
            <div class="col-4">Peter Browning</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item row">
          <div class="row">
            <img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w342//klNx4UqkcE9u7P3vsg20AKwgplw.jpg" class="col-1"/>
            <div class="col-7">Michael Caine</div>
            <div class="col-4">Stephen Miles</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item row">
          <div class="row">
            <img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w342//k4OiYIhr886ollgOrvrBs2ZIZbc.jpg" class="col-1"/>
            <div class="col-7">Dileep Rao</div>
            <div class="col-4">Yusuf</div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
